name: Lobec Web Diver
description: The future is coming! Get your gear ready for an adventure with Lobec, The Web Diver! They are equipped with weapons and vehicles from the future and set out to explore the system zone of the future Ngarengat World! But unfortunately, they were blocked by The Master Octopus, God of the system, who detected the presence of a Web Diver and tried to catch it, so that system data would not leak, and Master Octopus would still control Ngarengat Universe!
